                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "The student obediently sat at the desk and decided to <open> the textbook to the right page."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "От сильного удивления мальчик широко <раскрыть> рот и замер на месте.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "From sheer surprise, the boy <opened> his mouth wide and froze in place."
                            }
